Package: lxqt-nvmonitor
Architecture: any
Depends: lxqt-panel (>= 2.3.0),
 nvidia-compute-utils,
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Suggests: nvidia-driver
Description: NVIDIA GPU monitor plugin for LXQt panel
 An LXQt panel plugin that displays NVIDIA GPU metrics as a scrolling
 graph. Supported metrics include GPU utilization, VRAM load, VRAM usage,
 temperature, and power usage.
 .
 Data is sourced from the NVML library (libnvidia-ml.so).
